00:12:12.350 --> 00:12:16.250
biased, it's skewed, you can see the performance actually is also better

213
00:12:16.290 --> 00:12:16.770
for white.

214
00:12:17.690 --> 00:12:21.650
Now, if we go to the right in this bar, we can see CTranspath, and we can

