00:13:21.950 --> 00:13:25.670
an AI system to do a specific task, what we now do is we

233
00:13:25.930 --> 00:13:29.770
learn to extract representations that are very generic, that can be used

234
00:13:29.810 --> 00:13:33.130
for many downstream tasks. So we just want to

235
00:13:33.510 --> 00:13:37.390
translate this small image into, again, this kind of an embedding, so a vector of

236
00:13:37.450 --> 00:13:37.810
numbers.

237
00:13:38.930 --> 00:13:42.770
And these numbers should describe in very general sense what we are

