00:19:33.034 --> 00:19:36.174
predict quite well whether the tumor has a KRAS mutation.

341
00:19:36.294 --> 00:19:39.654
So you can see here it has an F1 score of 0.85.

342
00:19:40.294 --> 00:19:41.054
It can also do

343
00:19:42.034 --> 00:19:45.914
histological grading. It can find other kinds of mutations.

344
00:19:47.034 --> 00:19:50.954
So these foundation models can be a great foundation to build all these downstream

345
00:19:51.734 --> 00:19:53.554
tasks that we may go into later.

346
00:19:55.134 --> 00:19:58.954
Another one you can see here. So this is predicting response of

347
00:19:58.994 --> 00:20:00.294
lung cancer to immune therapy.

348
00:20:01.174 --> 00:20:05.064
What you can see here is if you do only images alone, you can see that it's

