00:22:05.774 --> 00:22:09.683
As I showed you before, if you combine text reports or captions with

385
00:22:09.734 --> 00:22:12.994
the images, you get to a more robust model, to a better

386
00:22:13.614 --> 00:22:14.274
performing model.

387
00:22:17.574 --> 00:22:20.924
But what I also showed, and this is a bit of a complicated graph, but what I also

