395
00:22:44.584 --> 00:22:47.994
And that is shown here very much. If you use a foundation model, you could do much

396
00:22:48.074 --> 00:22:51.914
better. Generalizability could be much better, but only if your

397
00:22:52.174 --> 00:22:56.074
model is robust enough. So it's very important that your model has a high quality

398
00:22:56.134 --> 00:22:57.794
and is trained on very diverse data.

