01:07:32.110 --> 01:07:36.050
clinicians have to use it and have to want it, right?

1186
01:07:36.670 --> 01:07:38.190
Otherwise, it's not going to be used.

1187
01:07:38.290 --> 01:07:41.210
So I'm very happy and proud to present

